QuestData.Title: Eye of Azshara: Into the Eye of Azshara
QuestData.Description:
Our investigation found that the naga, under the orders of Queen Azshara herself, are preparing to summon a powerful entity to unleash Azshara's power across the Broken Isles.
Travel to the Eye of Azshara, and put a stop to the ritual.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat the Wrath of Azshara in Eye of Azshara.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat the Wrath of Azshara in Eye of Azshara
